++ Open

Open is when data is loaded in some way.
    * The StandardizedScreens for open is the [Chooser].
      If a file that the application cannot open is selected, the appropriate application is loaded instead.
    * [Open] occurs on [Save]d items.
    * Displays [Loading] progress.

Files can be opened programmatically in different modes. These have [Extensibility] so that new ones can be implemented.
    * [Scanning]
    * [Indexing]
    * Read (low level)
    * Write (low level)

Files in LogicalMemory have a StandardRepresentations for clarity. For example, an overlay icon may appear ontop.

